        <title>Gemini2.5 Pro生成的SVG代码封神了，提示词一键直出PPT</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/gemini2.5-pro%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84svg%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%B0%81%E7%A5%9E%E4%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E8%AF%8D%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%B4%E5%87%BAppt/</link>
